#: tadv_admin.php:176
msgid "The toolbars in the Classic Paragraph and Classic blocks are narrower and show on focus."
msgstr "[傳統段落] 及 [傳統編輯器] 區塊中的工具列較窄，且僅顯示重點按鈕。"

#: tadv_admin.php:173
